New release of ledit (version 1.4), line editor for interactive commands,
written in Ocaml.

Changes
   Added M-backspace or M-delete : backward-kill-word
   Tabulations are expanded
   Option -c optionnal: "ledit comm args" <=> "ledit -c comm args"
   Fixed bug printing of characters ascii between 128 and 159

Available by ftp:
   ftp://ftp.inria.fr/INRIA/Projects/cristal/Daniel.de_Rauglaudre/
Files:
   README.ledit
   ledit.tar.gz

